@page
@model woodgrove_bank.HelpModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Help";
}

<h1 style="padding-bottom: 15px; padding-top: 15px;">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<div class="container">


    Woodgrove Bank is a live demo web application created by Microsoft to demonstrate several Microsoft Entra external
    ID features. it simulates an financial online service to both individual consumers
    and business customers. Allowing you to sign-up and sign-in by using Microsoft Entra Exteranl ID and to explore
    Microsoft Entra external ID’s capabilities in scenarios for financial institutions.

    <br />&nbsp;<br />

    <h3>Select a use case</h3>

    From the right corner of the page, select the <b>About the demo</b> button. <br />

    <img src="~/images/help/help-button.png"
        style="border-color: rgb(200, 200, 200); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 5px 5px 5px 5px ; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; width: 65%;">
    <br />
    Select a use case <br />

    <img src="~/images/help/select-button.png"
        style="border-color: rgb(200, 200, 200); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 5px 5px 5px 5px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
    <br />
    Read the instructions and start the use case<br />

    <img src="~/images/help/start-use-case.png"
        style="border-color: rgb(200, 200, 200); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 5px 5px 5px 5px;">

    <h3 style="padding-top: 25px;">Community Help and Support</h3>
    If you find a bug, notice something but are not sure how to solve it, or want to provide product feedback, please
    raise an issue on <a href="https://github.com/microsoft/woodgrove-bank/issues">GitHub Issues</a>.

    <br />&nbsp;<br />
    App version: @System.Reflection.Assembly.GetExecutingAssembly().GetName().Version.ToString()
</div>